more than anyone else.

954
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:32,800
I guarantee with my 30 years
of experience as a prosecutor.

955
00:43:34,599 --> 00:43:36,239
I believe that Lin Zhitao

956
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:38,880
